title: Selling the Skyline
description: This week Matt bids a farewell to his R32 Skyline, we deride picky DeLorean owners as Matt's car goes up on Bring a Trailer, discuss Top Gear and review the base 997.2 Porsche Carrera.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
